				</p>

				<div class="rounded-2xl border backdrop-blur shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-black/5 bg-neutral-900/70 border-white/10">
					<ol class="divide-y divide-gray-100/70">
						<li class="p-6 md:p-8 flex gap-5">
